ansible--version [to check version]

sudo apt install ansibe-core

sudo apt-get install vim [to install vim editor pacakge]

vim filenmae.yml (ESC + :q! to exit vim editor) [to open vim editor]

nano filename.yml [to open a nano editor]

ansible-playbook filename.yml [to run playbook]

ansibe-playbook <filename.yml>--syntax-check [to check syntax errors]



Docker Container:

docker run [to start a new docker  container from an image]
docker stop [to stop a running docker conatainer ID]
docker rm [to remove a docker conatainer]
docker ps [to list all the docker conatainers]
docker exec -it <container_ID> /bin/bash [accesing the container and id will be found when ps command is used]